title: Ned Rifle 2014 WEB-DL Sonata Premiere
description: Henry Fool and Fay Grim's son Ned sets out to find and kill his father for destroying his mother's life. But his aims are frustrated by the troublesome, sexy, and hilarious Susan, whose connection to Henry predates even his arrival in the lives of the Grim family. A funny, sad, and sexy adventure, Ned Rifle is an intellectually stimulating and compassionate satire. (C) Possible Films
